---
title: What are the system requirements for Pokémon Studio?
seoDescription: The system requirements to use Pokémon Studio
publishDate: '2022-09-15 18:10:00'
order: 0
---

Here is the list of operating systems required to use Pokémon Studio:

- Windows 10 and newer.
- Linux Ubuntu 14.04 and newer.
- Linux Fedora 24 and newer.
- Linux Debian 8 and newer.
- MacOS 10.11 (El Capitan) and newer. _MacOS version will come later._

**Note:** You need a 64Bits CPU.

